original_title: NPP wins in Kandy, Haputale, Weligama, Kotmale and Laggala
original_body_lines: The National People’s Power (NPP) has secured victory in the Kandy polling division in Kandy District, Laggala polling division in Matale District, Haputale polling division in Badulla District and Weligama polling division in Matara District.
